simulated data for the continuous approach (1D)

Source: R/mro1D.R
mro1D.Rd

A data set containing data simulated with constant recovery probability in one-dimensional space and continuous estimates of all parameters.

data(mro1D)

Format

A markRecaptureObject.

mro1D

An object of the type markRecaptureObject containing the simulated data with the true values of the parameters and the estimated values of the continuous approach

References

This data set was artificially created for the CONSURE package.

Examples


data(mro1D)
